verbose_text: On the other hand, cells exposed to MG evidenced a 3-fold increase in RAGE (receptor for advanced glycation end products) and a 2-fold increase in NF-kappaB (nuclear factor kappa-light-chain-enhancer of activated B cells) expression compared to control cells.
